CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Bankruptcy Proceedings – Exemptions From Execution – Residential Real
3 Property
4 FOR the purpose of providing that the exemption for exempting certain providing that the
5 exemption for owner–occupied residential real property from execution on a
6 judgment in certain amounts and subject to certain adjustments in a bankruptcy
7 proceeding includes certain real property held in a revocable trust; altering the
8 amount of the exemption for owner–occupied residential real property in a bankruptcy
9 proceeding includes certain real property held in a revocable trust; altering the
10 amount of the exemption for owner–occupied residential real property in a
11 bankruptcy proceeding; and generally relating to debtor exemptions and bankruptcy
12 proceedings.
13 BY repealing and reenacting, without amendments,
14 Article – Estates and Trusts
